{"tid":1406242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙一役真係影響深遠","createTime":"2019-08-04T12:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:14:54.000Z","uid":34478,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c36dcf363353a48d2f6116ca7701ac8733f300","tid":1406242,"uid":34478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:43:24.000Z","msg":"大批示威者由西區轉到銅鑼灣　佔據崇光對出軒尼詩道<br />\n<br />\n一批示威者在晚上乘坐港鐵由香港大學站前往銅鑼灣站，在崇光百貨對出聚集，佔據軒尼詩道，部分巴士及電車一度未能駛走，其後示威人士開路，讓部分巴士及電車離開。示威者以鐵馬、圍欄、垃圾桶及雪糕筒在軒尼詩道、以及軒尼詩道與波斯富街交界設置路障。亦有人帶來一批物資，包括<span style=\"color: red;\">不鏽鋼碟。</span><br />\n<br />\nRTHK新聞 2019-08-04 20:32:28<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21478166171da23f2aa709e969d2053a995c809b","tid":1406242,"uid":71505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:02:51.000Z","msg":"竟然會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d152b768c78476dd4bb9b4fa109539b5aa4c081a","tid":1406242,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"